{"tid":1217132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：警方使用低殺傷力武器","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T09:05:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5b8fabc9e1224c9f9002127bc856f3c2c65e65","tid":1217132,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰指，警方在昨日金鐘的警民衝突中拘捕11人，涉及公眾地方擾亂秩序、襲警及與暴動有關等罪行，亦有22名警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n他以暴徒形容昨日的示威者，又指警方所用的武器是低殺傷力。"},{"pid":"1f407163c562ea6bcc3bb8bde5371006a8a1a568","tid":1217132,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=351614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351614&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3948d90f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351614&h=f3ecb032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=351614</a>"},{"pid":"bd5ef812a54af47e21f2a2d4d1c54fc83509aac7","tid":1217132,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"我信係低殺傷力武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2299277576830901%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d59323fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/</a><br />\n<br />\n612嗰日一位16歲女學生嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議大家可以聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完之後我好嬲，亦都好想喊，香港今時今日嘅景況，除咗班高官之外，班蓄生警犬亦都有份一手一腳造成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映：</span></span><br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0f3d285c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4daf11e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0b6e191b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=70b14391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=6664f174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3d0d5762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n事後嚟張大合照慶功先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BUJgDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BUJgDg.png&h=d811719e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議告上聯合國！向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},{"pid":"466475f5375fcface64d23b5f7121de1628e5c0d","tid":1217132,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"低殺傷力？ 試下調轉我射你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f55eb6c37b47aee68ba1902ddc271c7e732d02","tid":1217132,"uid":74685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"低殺傷力=有殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有殺傷力=可殺可傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d1dff1e55100d43d1343619fde6ce7fe8f843b","tid":1217132,"uid":128805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n燃燒彈冇<br />\n冇燒車<br />\n玻璃都冇爆<br />\n警察皮外傷都冇聽過<br />\n<br />\n你就齊裝又警棍又催淚彈又開槍打到人嘔晒血<br />\n然後我係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a680915f5dcca92b19fffac5f6351a83580224","tid":1217132,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"比起用坦克車？都算嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7969bd8b32d764a7c684227950cc11596935b1d","tid":1217132,"uid":155789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"與政府高層無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1584a239e2e614c5de8a9724695c0820d7fae6","tid":1217132,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi